review_blob: For me this beer has something incredible even if its not like it was ... I cant describe it but thats like a souvenir about my life in France. This dark bier, with a lot of different flavors, so many that is very difficult to explain all of them, the foam not really white not brown, may be cream will be the best to describe the color, arf ... I have just a word for that : tate it and you will never forget it !! nothing to compare to the most common bier in USA. So strong that three of them is enough for your night !!!(its a pity to drink three of them in the same night, you will taste only the first one ... ).
